Dialogue: 1,1:29:53.70,1:29:55.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯！我才不會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.70,1:29:55.66,Line JP,,0,0,0,,うん！　負けるもんかいね
Dialogue: 1,1:29:55.66,1:29:57.59,Line CN,,0,0,0,,新子！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.66,1:29:57.59,Line JP,,0,0,0,,新子ちゃん！
